-- ds.h2: `is_empty(a: any) ⚠️`

This is FScript function. It gives if the value passed to argument `a` is null or empty.

-- ds.rendered: Sample code using `is_empty()`

-- ds.rendered.input:

\-- optional string name:

\-- ftd.text: name is empty
if: { is_empty(name) } ;; <hl>

\-- string list names:

\-- ftd.text: There is no name in names
if: { is_empty(names) } ;; <hl>

-- ds.rendered.output:

-- is-empty-sample:

-- end: ds.rendered.output

-- end: ds.rendered











